<div class="hgroup"><h1 class="title">File Server</h1></div>
<div class="region">
<div class="contents">
<p class="para">最通用的连接 Ubuntu 和 Windows的方法之一是将 Samba 配置为文件服务器。本部分包括设置Samba&gt;服务器以便同 Windows 客户端共享文件。</p>
<p class="para">
    The server will be configured to share files with any client on the network without prompting for a password.  If
    your environment requires stricter Access Controls see <a class="xref" href="samba-fileprint-security.html" title="Securing File and Print Server">Securing File and Print Server</a>.
    </p>
</div>
<div class="links sectionlinks" role="navigation"><ul>
<li class="links"><a class="xref" href="samba-fileserver.html#samba-fileserver-installation" title="安装">安装</a></li>
<li class="links"><a class="xref" href="samba-fileserver.html#samba-fileserver-configuration" title="配置">配置</a></li>
<li class="links"><a class="xref" href="samba-fileserver.html#samba-fileserver-resources" title="资源">资源</a></li>
</ul></div>
<div class="sect2 sect" id="samba-fileserver-installation"><div class="inner">
<div class="hgroup"><h2 class="title">安装</h2></div>
<div class="region"><div class="contents">
<p class="para">第一步是安装samba软件包。在终端提示符键入：</p>
<div class="screen"><pre class="contents "><span class="cmd command">sudo apt install samba</span>
</pre></div>
<p class="para">这是唯一需要做的；现在您可以通过配置 Samba 来共享文件了。</p>
</div></div>
</div></div>
<div class="sect2 sect" id="samba-fileserver-configuration"><div class="inner">
<div class="hgroup"><h2 class="title">配置</h2></div>
<div class="region"><div class="contents">
<p class="para">
      The main Samba configuration file is located in <span class="file filename">/etc/samba/smb.conf</span>.  The default configuration file
      has a significant number of comments in order to document various configuration directives.  
      </p>
<div class="note" title="备注"><div class="inner"><div class="region"><div class="contents">
        <p class="para">不是所有可行的选项都包括在默认配置文件中。请参见<span class="file filename">smb.conf</span><span class="app application">man</span> 手册页，或者 <a href="http://samba.org/samba/docs/man/Samba-HOWTO-Collection/" class="ulink" title="http://samba.org/samba/docs/man/Samba-HOWTO-Collection/">Samba HOWTO 合集</a></p>
      </div></div></div></div>
<div class="steps"><div class="inner"><ol class="steps">
<li class="steps">

        <p class="para">首先，编辑<span class="file filename">/etc/samba/smb.conf</span>文件中的<span class="em emphasis">[global]</span>片段的键值对</p>

<div class="code"><pre class="contents ">   工作组 = EXAMPLE
   ...
   安全等级 = user
</pre></div>

        <p class="para"><span class="em emphasis">security</span>这个参数在[global]章节的下面，默认是被注释掉的。同样，根据你的环境改变<span class="em emphasis">EXAMPLE</span>参数。</p>

        </li>
<li class="steps">
  
        <p class="para">在文件底部为要共享的目录创建一个新段落或将某一例子前#去掉，</p>

<div class="code"><pre class="contents ">[share]
    说明 = Ubuntu File Server Share
    路径 = /srv/samba/share
    可浏览 = yes
    客人访问 = yes
    只读 = no
    create mask = 0755
</pre></div>

      <div class="list itemizedlist"><ul class="list itemizedlist">
<li class="list itemizedlist">
          <p class="para"><span class="em emphasis">comment:</span> 一段简短的描述，根据你的需要进行调整。</p>
        </li>
<li class="list itemizedlist">
          <p class="para"><span class="em emphasis">path:</span>共享文件的路径</p>
          <p class="para">这个例子使用的文件是 <span class="file filename">/srv/samba/sharename</span> 因为按照 <span class="em emphasis">文件系统层次结构标准(FHS)</span>
<a href="http://www.pathname.com/fhs/pub/fhs-2.3.html#SRVDATAFORSERVICESPROVIDEDBYSYSTEM" class="ulink" title="http://www.pathname.com/fhs/pub/fhs-2.3.html#SRVDATAFORSERVICESPROVIDEDBYSYSTEM">/srv</a> 站点提供的数据。技术上来说Samba shares只要权限正确，可以在文件系统的任何位置，但是建议遵守规范。</p>
        </li>
<li class="list itemizedlist">
          <p class="para"><span class="em emphasis">browsable:</span> 允许windows客户机使用资源管理器浏览共享目录。</p>
        </li>
<li class="list itemizedlist">
          <p class="para"><span class="em emphasis">guest ok:</span>允许客户机连接共享目录不用提供密码。</p>
        </li>
<li class="list itemizedlist">
          <p class="para"><span class="em emphasis">只读::</span>决定共享是否为只读或已赋予写权限。只有当其值为<span class="em emphasis">no</span>时才会赋予写权限，就如此例中所看到的。如果值是<span class="em emphasis">yes</span>，那么将只能以只读方式进入。</p>
        </li>
<li class="list itemizedlist">
          <p class="para"><span class="em emphasis">create mask:</span> 在文件被创建时确定新建文件的权限。</p>
        </li>
</ul></div>

      </li>
<li class="steps">
        
        <p class="para">既然<span class="app application">Samba</span>已经设置，您需要新建一个目录并更改授权。请从终端输入：</p>

<div class="screen"><pre class="contents "><span class="cmd command">sudo mkdir -p /srv/samba/share</span>
<span class="cmd command">sudo chown nobody:nogroup /srv/samba/share/</span>
</pre></div>

      <div class="note" title="备注"><div class="inner"><div class="region"><div class="contents">
        <p class="para"><span class="em emphasis">-p</span> 开关使 mkdir 创建整个目录，如果该目录不存在。</p>
      </div></div></div></div>

      </li>
<li class="steps">
     
      <p class="para">最后，为使新设定生效，请重启<span class="app application">samba</span>服务。</p>

<div class="screen"><pre class="contents "><span class="cmd command">sudo systemctl restart smbd.service nmbd.service</span>
</pre></div>

      </li>
</ol></div></div>
<div class="note note-warning" title="警告"><div class="inner"><div class="region"><div class="contents">
        <p class="para">再次地，上述设定使得所有用户可以接入本地网络。欲知更多安全设定方法请参阅<a class="xref" href="samba-fileprint-security.html" title="Securing File and Print Server">Securing File and Print Server</a>。</p>
      </div></div></div></div>
<p class="para">在一个 Windows 客户端里，你应该可以看见 Ubuntu 文件服务器和共享文件夹。如果你的客户端没有自动显示，请您在
 Windows 文件管理器中使用服务器的IP地址连接到服务器，比如：\\192.168.1.1。如果想要实验是否能够正常使用，您可以在
 Windows 下为服务器创建一个文件夹来测试服务器是否正常工作。</p>
<p class="para">为了创建更多的共享只需在文件 <span class="file filename">/etc/samba/smb.conf</span>中的章节下写入新的路径，并重新启动 <span class="em emphasis">Samba</span>。只需要确定该目录要共享和当前的权限是正确的。</p>
<div class="note" title="备注"><div class="inner"><div class="region"><div class="contents">
        <p class="para">共享名 <span class="em emphasis">"[share]"</span> 和 </p>
      </div></div></div></div>
</div></div>
</div></div>
